<P>
Photo, Umpire Bill Hohn's bad news for Dodgers' Mickey Hatcher is good for 
Padres' Bip Roberts after Hatcher was thrown out by Tony Gwynn trying to 
stretch a single into a double in first inning. BOB GRIESER / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
